
Cross-compiling openGalaxy on a Debian or Ubuntu computer:
==========================================================

 (See also: README-BUILDING)

 $ tar xf opengalaxy-0.15.tar.xz && cd opengalaxy-0.15
 $ mkdir build-rpi-stable && cd build-rpi-stable
 $ ../build-debs raspbian stable armhf ../../opengalaxy-0.15.tar.xz

 Instead of 'stable' you can also use a specific version like
 'jessie' or 'stretch'.

